text: Blackstreet is an American R&B; group. It began around 1991. It was created through Teddy Riley. The group was very strong during the 1990s. Their songs included "No Diggity" and "Booty Call". == Albums == * Blackstreet (1994) * Another Level (1996) * Finally (1999) * Level II (2003) == Tours == * Blackstreet Tour (1994-1995) * Another Level Tour (1997) * Finally Tour (1999-2000) * Level II Tour (2003-2004) category:1990s American music groups category:American R&B; bands
